long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Welcome to Launchify, a demo Chrome extension that showcases the power of our boilerplate code. This extension is a live example of what you can achieve with our boilerplate code, available at https://www.launchify.club

Features:

New tab page currently with Launchify branding 
Side panel with Launchify branding
Basic UI, background script, and content script demonstrations
